          <h5>What is Do Art Daily?</h5>
          <p>Do Art Daily is the third, and hopefully last, iteration of the "Last Artist Standing" 
            endeavor. In essence, the mission of this project, and by extension, this website is to 
            encourage the artistic growth of all its participants. This is done by reinforcing the habit 
            of practicing, facilitated by simply tracking your "streak", or consecutive periods in which 
            you worked on your art. Moreover, users are a part of a community that continues to provide 
            friendly competition, constructive criticism and inspiration.<br><br>
            Over time, additional features, such as badges, challenges, and topic prompts (to be
            implemented soon) have been implemented across the sites, helping keep users out of their
            comfort zone, allowing users to explore subjects they are interested in, or simply acting 
            as additional impetuses to just keep drawing.<br><br>
            <span style="font-weight: 600">To put it simply, our mission is to encourage all artists, 
            of all disciplines and skill levels, to persist in their craft, and find fulfillment in 
            the process.</span>
          </p>
